    264          /*
    265           *********************************************************************************************************
    266           *                                            temperTask()
    267           *
    268           * Description : Measure a person's temperature
    269           *
    270           * Argument(s) : p
    271           *
    272           * Return(s)   : none.
    273           *
    274           * Caller(s)   : This is a task.
